result.name: Pepper Lunch

reviews.text: Very poor Hygiene. Floor is dirty and tables and menus are oily and sticky. They don’t give a dam. Ask them to clean it and they’ll do so with a wet soaked towel leaving the table wet. Raw meat is handled here, it’s worisome if the sake hygiene standards apply behind kitchen doors

Good choice for a simple yet tasty meal. Be seated first and order your choice at the counter and pay. Staffs will deliver the dishes to your table. Mix all with your choice of sauce garlic peper or honey mustard while it is hot. The waiting queue is long in meal time, but it is worthy. Three choices of beef, chicken or salmon.
Hot plates of tasty simple food
